      "title": "SJB says will attend only Speaker summoned party leaders meeting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The main Opposition  Samagi Jana Balawegaya said it will attending only the Speaker summoned party leaders meeting and not that convened by Prime Minister",
        "\"A Party Leaders' Meeting is summoned by Speaker and not by PM. We will be attending the Party Leaders' Meeting summoned by the Speaker,\" a SJB spokesman told the Daily FT."
      ],
